Offline,Geolocation,allows,cellphones,to,derive,a,location,without,being,connected,to,the,internet,or,data,networks,The,service,is,designed,as,a,failover,system,when,a,user,has,no,Internet,connection,due,to,roaming,or,coverage,issues,and,GPS,has,not,been,turned,on,or,is,not,available,indoors,The,Offline,Geolocation,developer,kit,allows,users,to,access,a,global,database,of,mobile,phone,cell,tower,locations,along,with,data,such,as,MCC,MNC,LAC,and,cellid,information,The,service,is,free,to,use